%A1t-m%E1%BB%99/poem-EEt23_2qhCX1iNw9CLgAkA">Mân thành phát mộ - 閩城發暮</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A1t-%C4%90%C3%B4-L%E1%BA%A1t/author-o6P2TdkwVUJwiHY0ASq8kw">Tát Đô Lạt</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Quang-Du%E1%BA%ABn/Tr%C3%BAc-chi-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-06/poem-fVODuC7wZwcIAgrpzpigFw">Trúc chi từ kỳ 06 - 竹枝詞其六</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Quang-Du%E1%BA%ABn/author-o4EVPW8qBqGIiDBnjz0VQg">Vương Quang Duẫn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nhi%E1%BA%BFp-Di-Trung/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-%C4%91i%E1%BB%81n-gia/poem-VO87hHw2By07pD71vLGG6g">Vịnh điền gia - 詠田家</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nhi%E1%BA%BFp-Di-Trung/author-JPBJfe6mzLjgKnSRDIIASg">Nhiếp Di Trung</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/Y%E1%BA%BFt-S%C6%A1n/poem-oH7Plkf-z--WaPfyFGZvaQ">Yết Sơn - 謁山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
